        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>pie mix</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (or 2!)</p><p>Top the pie mix with the <strong>rolled pastry </strong>and crimp round the edge with a fork</p><p>Score a cross in the middle of the pastry and put it in the oven for 20-22 min or until puffed up and golden and the meat is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>venison, pork & red wine pie</strong></p>",
